end of the country. But no, he’s only applying to ones in London, even though
his teachers were desperate for him to try for Oxbridge. He’s staying in
London so he can live here and look after us and make sure we’re al right.’
Kit manages to pul off a sardonic laugh. ‘You’re deluded, Maya. You know
