‘Leila, yes, his sister, good idea. See if you can find her, wil you?’
Time hiccups; it is either later or sooner, I can’t tel which. The nurse has
arrived, I’m not sure why
– I’m confused about everything now. Maybe I was wrong. Maybe they are
actualy trying to help me. Mrs Shah’s got a stethoscope in her ears and is
