the little ones are not yet asleep. But by the time they are, Kit is roaming the
house, looking for food or watching TV, and by the time he finaly goes to bed
Maya is passed out in hers.
Half-term brings little respite. It rains al week and, cooped up inside with no
money for outings or even the cinema, Tiffin and Wila bicker constantly
