long-term damage – she won’t even need a plaster cast and her shoulder wil
be back to normal in a week or possibly even less! They said dislocated
shoulders happen to children al the time, that it’s realy quite common, they
see it al the time, it’s nothing to worry about!’ He is speaking insanely fast,
