‘She dislocated her shoulder?’ I gasp.
He flinches, as if stung by the words. ‘Yeah, but that’s al! Nothing else!
They’ve X-rayed her and everything and—’
‘What happened?’
‘She just fel off the kitchen counter!’ He tries to touch me but I move out of
